    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You inject a surge of chakra into your eyes increasing your visual perception, making it look like the world is slowing down around you. You do not spend chakra to maintain concentration with this jutsu. For the duration, creatures whom you can see within range actions seemingly slow down to a crawl. Melee Weapons attacks or Hebi Clan Bukijutsu you cast cannot be made at disadvantage and creatures within range cannot gain advantage against any Hebi Clan Bukijutsu. </p>",
